            <abstract encodinganalog="520" label="Abstract">The Adams mss., 1912-1981, consist of
                letters, photographs, and writings by and about Booth Tarkington, author of
                Indianapolis and Kennebunkport, Maine, collected by Reily Gibson Adams, whose wife
                was a relative of Tarkington.</abstract>
